org.icefaces.ace.component.column

Interface IProxiableColumn

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IColumn
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Column, ProxiedBodyColumn

    public interface IProxiableColumn
extends IColumn
    To fully support ColumnGroup headers, there needs to be a connection between each Column component in the body and its corresponding Column component in the header ColumnGroup. Via a proxy, properties may be accessed and set, so that they don't have to be redundantly specified on each. In the simplest case, there is no header ColumnGroup, and the body column itself implements this interface.
